        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Five affirmations for the person who keeps filling the week before they have protected any of it. Read each one slowly, then read them all again."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The practice"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "No is a complete sentence."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Saying no to this is saying yes to what is already mine."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "My time has weight. No is how I hold it."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I can say no and stay kind. The two are not in conflict."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The no I give today is how I show up fully for what I have already committed to."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
